WEBVTT

01:02.938 --> 01:07.485
Story: WONG JING
Screenplay: THE PEACE (WO PING) GROUP

01:17.828 --> 01:21.707
Assistant Directors:
LEE CHA, HO LIN-CHOW, FONG LEE-KWAN

01:24.335 --> 01:28.255
Lighting: TANG MING
Props: LEUNG WING (YIM)
Costumes: LIU CHI-YU

01:29.381 --> 01:33.135
Dialogue: DING YUE, WONG PING
Sound Effects: NG KWOK-WAH

01:34.386 --> 01:37.807
Editor: PETER CHEUNG YIU-CHUNG
Music: FRANKIE CHAN FAN-KEI
